Components Required:
Arduino Uno
IR Sensor Module
Buzzer
LED (Optional, for visual alert)
Resistor (220 ohms for the LED)
Jumper wires
Breadboard




Wiring Diagram

:
IR Sensor Module:
VCC → Arduino 5V
GND → Arduino GND
OUT → Arduino Digital Pin 2

Buzzer:
Positive (long leg) → Arduino Digital Pin 9 (via resistor, if needed)
Negative (short leg) → Arduino GND


LED (Optional):
Anode (long leg) → Arduino Digital Pin 10 (via 220-ohm resistor)
Cathode (short leg) → Arduino GND
